text:
Hi <@U02J3F33CVA>, did you define a group-style?
If so, the style can only apply inside its own module and it requires to be written inside a scope_css like this


&lt;style&gt;
{% scope_css %}
  .content .title div{
    color: {{ module.style.font.color }};
  }
{% end_scope_css %}
&lt;/style&gt;
